{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"A few years ago, my eyes were opened"},{"time":3000,"text":"to the dark side of the construction industry."},{"time":6000,"text":"In 2006, young Qatari students"},{"time":9000,"text":"took me to go and see the migrant worker camps."},{"time":11000,"text":"And since then I've followed the unfolding issue of worker rights."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"In the last six months, more than 300 skyscrapers"},{"time":18000,"text":"in the UAE have been put on hold or canceled."},{"time":21000,"text":"Behind the headlines that lay behind these buildings"},{"time":24000,"text":"is the fate of the often-indentured construction worker."},{"time":28000,"text":"1.1 million of them."},{"time":30000,"text":"Mainly Indian, Pakistani, Sri Lankan"},{"time":33000,"text":"and Nepalese, these laborers risk everything"},{"time":35000,"text":"to make money for their families back home."},{"time":38000,"text":"They pay a middle-man thousands of dollars to be there."},{"time":40000,"text":"And when they arrive, they find themselves in labor camps with no water,"},{"time":44000,"text":"no air conditioning, and their passports taken away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"While it's easy to point the finger at local officials and higher authorities,"},{"time":52000,"text":"99 percent of these people are hired by the private sector,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and so therefore we're equally, if not more, accountable."},{"time":59000,"text":"Groups like Buildsafe UAE have emerged,"},{"time":62000,"text":"but the numbers are simply overwhelming."},{"time":64000,"text":"In August 2008,"},{"time":66000,"text":"UAE public officials noted"},{"time":68000,"text":"that 40 percent of the country's 1,098 labor camps"},{"time":72000,"text":"had violated minimum health and fire safety regulations."},{"time":75000,"text":"And last summer, more than 10,000 workers"},{"time":78000,"text":"protested for the non-payment of wages,"},{"time":81000,"text":"for the poor quality of food, and inadequate housing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"And then the financial collapse happened."},{"time":87000,"text":"When the contractors have gone bust,"},{"time":89000,"text":"as they've been overleveraged like everyone else,"},{"time":91000,"text":"the difference is everything goes missing,"},{"time":94000,"text":"documentation, passports,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and tickets home for these workers."},{"time":98000,"text":"Currently, right now, thousands of workers are abandoned."},{"time":102000,"text":"There is no way back home."},{"time":104000,"text":"And there is no way, and no proof of arrival."},{"time":107000,"text":"These are the boom-and-bust refugees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"The question is, as a building professional,"},{"time":113000,"text":"as an architect, an engineer, as a developer,"},{"time":115000,"text":"if you know this is going on,"},{"time":117000,"text":"as we go to the sights every single week,"},{"time":120000,"text":"are you complacent or complicit"},{"time":122000,"text":"in the human rights violations?"},{"time":124000,"text":"So let's forget your environmental footprint."},{"time":127000,"text":"Let's think about your ethical footprint."},{"time":129000,"text":"What good is it"},{"time":132000,"text":"to build a zero-carbon, energy efficient complex,"},{"time":135000,"text":"when the labor producing this architectural gem"},{"time":138000,"text":"is unethical at best?"},{"time":141000,"text":"Now, recently I've been told I've been taking the high road."},{"time":143000,"text":"But, quite frankly, on this issue,"},{"time":145000,"text":"there is no other road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"So let's not forget who is really paying the price of this financial collapse."},{"time":151000,"text":"And that as we worry about our next job in the office,"},{"time":154000,"text":"the next design that we can get, to keep our workers."},{"time":158000,"text":"Let's not forget these men, who are truly dying to work."},{"time":161000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":163000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}